== About me
I am a Research Assistant Professor at the Department of Electrical and Electronic Engineering, The University of Hong Kong.
I received my Ph.D. degree in Information Engineering from The Chinese University of Hong Kong in 2025, supervised by [https://staff.ie.cuhk.edu.hk/~yjzhang/ Prof. Angela Yingjun Zhang].
Before that, I received my B.Eng. degree from the Yingcai Honors College, University of Electronic Science and Technology of China in 2021, advised by [https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=o6W_m00AAAAJ&hl=en Prof. Xiaojun Yuan].
My research focuses on signal processing and machine learning for wireless communications, with a particular emphasis on the convergence of model-based algorithms and data-driven learning toward white-box and explainable AI solutions for future wireless networks.


